.TH FINDREDUNDANTDEPS 1 "PKGMAINT-#VERSION# Manual"

.SH NAME
findredundantdeps - find unnecessary dependencies of a source package

.SH SYNOPSIS
findredundantdeps \fIPKG\fR

.SH DESCRIPTION
findredundantdeps prints the full recursive dependencies of a given
\fIPKG\fR displaying the dependencies that are already contained in
the depending package.
.PP
This script requires \fBpkgman\fR(8).

.SH SEE ALSO
\fBfinddeps\fR(1), \fBpkgman\fR(1).
